Ottoken-1-
Tokens are special items found in Crash Team Racing, Crash Nitro Kart and Crash Team Racing Nitro-Fueled where players need them in order to be able to take part in Gem Cups. In CTR, tokens come in five colors: red, blue, yellow, green and purple. In CNK, they come in only four colors as there is no yellow one.



ADVERTISEMENT
Ways to get them
The method used to obtain tokens varies slightly between CTR and CNK, and the purple tokens have a different obtain method in both games.

Crash Team Racing
In CTR, players need to get the letters C, T, and R in a race, and come in first place to win a token.
